name: Cat Montiel
text: I LOVE Pizza Hut, it's my favorite pizza, hands down. So why the 1 star? Becausr the one in my town closed for good in the middle of the night with no warning whatsoever. Boo, Fostoria Pizza Hut owner!

name: Sledgeman
text: Friendly staff and the food is typical for Pizza Hut.  The restaurant is clean and you feel, "safe" eating there.  I wish they still had the buffet though.

name: Harold Bishop
text: It's a pizza place. The quality of food was OK.

name: Erin W
text: I used to love this place but had a really bad service this time. Won't be returning.
